## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of the sources reviewed. Some articles may not reflect the most current developments in anti-ableism efforts. Additionally, the complexity of ableism as a societal issue means that its full impact may not be entirely captured within the constraints of this report. Further research is recommended to explore the intersectionality of ableism with other forms of discrimination.